？<br />\n<br />\n大家如果要指責，請向政府指責，而唔係好似呢幅漫畫「某文化」咁，反而指責為人民向奴隸主抗爭嘅示威者。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/saa7Rku.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsaa7Rku.png&h=58898183&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b74cca95b702359d33af15d9897b853c05c3cb45","tid":1410022,"uid":226955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9ad27735e8a06d05107e8de6f3521ea426934e77","tid":1410022,"uid":53003,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"90fd79d8a1f94ad2194fede0c9961d998892dbb5","tid":1410022,"uid":15590,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:30:20.000Z","msg":"啱啱個女人on9到<br />\n話混亂但講極都係話示威者唔好<br />\n冇理過政府、警犬做嘅嘢<br />\n痴線"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:37:44.000Z","msg":"其實好正常，好多人唔會諗遠因，所以大家要講解"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:40:24.000Z","msg":"呢個係犬儒人格"},{"pid":"eaedf0b759994efb0ad04bb6450fb31477ab76a0","tid":1410022,"uid":69535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:41:30.000Z","msg":"有冇人會打電話去881?"},{"pid":"2dd5f93f0c6c411d02df0283d949c5c8957d4da7","tid":1410022,"uid":19279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:44:35.000Z","msg":"呢個老闆 講到好似想喊咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a757cfa0fea9ed24245a553ee31d5fc96978eb2e","tid":1410022,"uid":285413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:50:41.000Z","msg":"教育性文宣不足，愚民就會有咁嘅反應<br />\n<br />\n大家做嘢喇，人人都可以係文宣人員!<br />\n<br />\n跪求大家入嚟幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><del><del>還原真相，教化愚民，<br />\n「滿貼十八區」教育工程文宣需要你!!!!!!!!!!<br />\n嚴重缺圖</del></del></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n(自行refer to)<br />\n(長期置頂)「滿貼十八區」教育工程文宣圖收集<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.